"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/578706","Department of Health","false","2016-09-13","<p>NHS England is an independent body which bases its annual provisional investment decisions on rigorous examination of existing evidence and cost benefit analyses. As such, ministers do not typically meet with NHS England to discuss specialised investment decisions.</p><p>However my noble Friend the Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State Lord Prior met with NHS England to discuss the overall strategy for specialised commissioning on 12 September 2016.</p><p>Officials continue to have ongoing discussions with NHS England regarding both provisional investment decisions and specialised services commissioning overall.</p>","Warrington South","David Mowat","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/578706/answer",,,,,,"2016-09-13T11:34:26.01Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/578706/answer","Biography information for David Mowat","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/578706/answer",,,,,"17","Health","Health","2016-09-08","Health Services","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, what discussions he has had with NHS England on the results of the provisional investment decisions for specialised services.","false","Biography information for Colleen Fletcher","Coventry North East","Colleen Fletcher","45615"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/578707","Cabinet Office","false","2016-09-13","<p>The information requested falls within the responsibility of the UK Statistics Authority. I have asked the Authority to reply.</p>","Kingswood","Chris Skidmore","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/578707/answer","PQ 45612 final.pdf","PQ 45612 final.pdf","UKSA Letter to Member - Diffuse Intrinsic Pontine ","UKSA Letter to Member - Diffuse Intrinsic Pontine ",,"2016-09-13T09:27:18.457Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/578707/answer","Biography information for Chris Skidmore","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/578707/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2016-09-08","Brain: Tumours","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, how many cases of Diffuse Intrinsic Pontine Glioma have been diagnosed in each of the last ten years.","false","Biography information for Wes Streeting","Ilford North","Wes Streeting","45612"
