"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/577484","Ministry of Defence","false","2016-09-12","<p>No contract was awarded to Lovell Partnerships in 2016. A contract was awarded in 2014, with the core purpose of constructing Service Family Accommodation in Stafford.</p>","Milton Keynes North","Mark Lancaster","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/577484/answer",,,,,,"2016-09-12T16:25:47.817Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/577484/answer","Biography information for Mark Lancaster","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/577484/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2016-09-07","Ministry of Defence: Lovell Partnership Homes","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, whether his Department's contract with Lovell Partnerships announced on 10 January 2016 is for purposes other than the building of new homes for soldiers.","false","Biography information for Clive Lewis","Norwich South","Clive Lewis","45337"
